Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是十天前发生的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}深夜的便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那里我遇到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没关系 不过你这样很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最好用篮子装
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}篮子？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:30.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦 原来可以用那个篮子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢您的提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么办 这下糟了 我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然会有人做出和透一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然我不清楚她指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.43,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还是用篮子来装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:01:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在我面前笑得那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:59.60,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我觉得心里暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想一直看着你笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们将来可以没个大人样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但一定要做一个对自己的言行负责的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽说做到这一点更难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:54.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作为教师 我要对你们说的就这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好享受你们的假期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诸位 终于等来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放暑假喽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姐要吃喝玩乐 睡觉 兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去你妈的学习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放假真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我现在连汽车都能揍翻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那样不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亚丽莎 请你不要太激动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然刚开始放假让你有些飘飘然 我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}确实 看到你这副造型我已经冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}花岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}补习日期已经贴在走廊上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可不需要去看那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毕竟我没有任何一门功课亮红灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪有人会乐意在大热天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跑来这种没空调的教室补习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说得对 回想去年真的太苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是因为这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然是这样 你每次都考及格不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是啊 为什么不每次考试都像这次一样努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关于这个我也有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是我一点动力也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:19.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是说我们像天空中飞舞的鸟儿一样自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 下午做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 我今天就得去做兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白天去咖啡馆 晚上去便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毕竟正是赚钱的好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我今年本来也想做更多兼职的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是没找到时间去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你现在可要操持那么大一片宅子里的家务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还要照顾三个大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你再去找更多的工作试试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过劳死才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不 受到照顾的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:05:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 话说你之前提到遇见了一个和透很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是在做哪个兼职时遇到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说过很多次了 他并不是长得像透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么说呢 他冒冒失失的样子让我想起了透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗 他有那么毛手毛脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冒冒失失？毛手毛脚？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说 我之后也没再遇见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以的话 我还想再见他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不管怎么说 刚放暑假真的好开心好激动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这人真的好单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人家可不想被真正单纯的人说成单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 我哪里单纯了 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学 路上顺便去买些做晚饭的菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么挑完衅就跑 臭老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么还没意识到自己单纯就单纯在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太容易被人带节奏呢 蠢猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个 听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}晚饭吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姜汁烧肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想吃姜汁烧肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泼 泼春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这是在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗 很凉快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你傻傻地站在喷泉下的样子在别人看来很渗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大热天淋点水再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这只猖狂的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苦夏就应该吃生姜烧肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.28,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全身都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:42.27,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次不会手下留情的 臭兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了庆祝暑假开始 今天大家一起出来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是红叶 这里是商场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先保密 到了就知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希你们也快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你缺少年轻人的朝气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不也没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听我说 是班上的女生告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说那里超好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我想带上大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那里很好玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 到了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哇 看起来真的很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里怎么看都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好期待啊 Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先听听其他人的想法 再决定进不进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比如 本田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经吓得说不出话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}免谈 咱们回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透 不可以吗 很害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 非要说害不害怕的话 应该说非常害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但俗话说「心静自然凉」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不能总是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实像这种情况躲躲也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我这就进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都看好了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请允许我入场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被这些纸糊的东西吓得哇哇大叫也是不易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么会被吓成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相比之下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这家伙走一路笑一路我也是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.60,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个人为什么倒吊着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.31,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}新的保健方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:39.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过我觉得笑也是一种很好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用笑声赶走惧怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么这么执着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶紧撤不就行了吗 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你更可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事已至此 那就闭着眼向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学 最好还是睁着眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是闭上眼好像就没那么害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还会被声音吓到 闭上眼有什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}该朝 该朝哪边走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样下去可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}撞到不该撞的地方 搞不好要出人命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我牵着你走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:37.44,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我牵着你走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}学我说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准模仿我 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁会去模仿一个笨蛋 会被傻气传染的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有下流气质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我既不是笨蛋也不下流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有你真的很碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们手牵手一起走吧 透
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么能把女孩子放在一边不管只顾吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}烦死人了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶紧走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过他说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田同学 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太害怕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可以给每个人编个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 编故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就比如说这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个人虽然看起来很吓人 但其实是个热心肠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是个喜欢动物和做菜的好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}休息日还会主动参加志愿活动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在邻里间的「最想和他结婚的男性」中排名第一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唯一的缺点就是泪点太低
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而 这位青年其实背负着一段沉痛的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他在十岁时被母亲抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在一个大雨倾盆的冰冷夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}温柔地为自己披上手打毛衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}温柔的双手 温柔的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼角的泪光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是他记忆中母亲最后的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第二天早上 母亲已离他而去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有醉醺醺的父亲 高额欠款
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以及那件手打毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但他相信那晚母亲的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从来都没有怨恨过母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从此 他毫无怨言地勤奋工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只为偿还父亲的欠债
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紧紧抱着那件浸染着母亲回忆的毛衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期待着将来有一天能和母亲重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而他的母亲今天也来这里看望他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们几个干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母亲离家出走也是有她的苦衷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而现在 母亲为当年的离开感到后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就让这位母亲亲口为我们讲述吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感动的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准搞破坏！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好个鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先给我数十个数再好好反省反省 混账东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 怎么能弄坏东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能找你们家长来赔偿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过这几个孩子怎么长得这么标致
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}模特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先站那等会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请等一下 我们会如数赔偿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请不要再把他们分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托你了 那两位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们俩是被迫分开的母子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是说了吗 不要把春的胡扯当真
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会被大叔笑话的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.11,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很久以前 在他还是个孩子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.40,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母亲丢下他离家出走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叔叔我很久没听到这么感人的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这人是笨蛋 这片儿住的都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}热死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么热的天 他们几个究竟跑哪儿玩去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的还能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:13:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还能再见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}便利店里的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 我就是便利店里的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太巧了吧 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没事吧 上气不接下气的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才看到你的背影 我怕又错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就拼命追了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是莫名其妙 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}午饭还没吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟了 再饿下去我又要发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也没吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不如咱们一起去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.63,0:14:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就当成是给便利店那次道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等我 山药泥荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:54.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白嫖一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只吃山药泥荞麦面就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最近迷上了山药泥荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也最好提前想好自己要吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}山药泥 山药泥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}久等 您的山药泥荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}名字吗 我叫红野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我叫鱼谷 鱼谷亚丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你路过那里是有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的 我只是随便逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}久等了 您的葱花鸭肉面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好不容易从工作中抽开身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但却没什么可做的 就随便走走打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你今天也在做兼职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 在咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还有一份便利店的兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我今年26了 你看起来还是高中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}高二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}年纪轻轻蛮能干的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里能干了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大我9岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是不是有点不合法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相比之下 那天是我第一次去便利店买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是献丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不知道该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到底谁呀 该不会是某国的国王陛下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是现今怎么可能还有人没去便利店买过东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且还是26岁的大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为对我来说没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那天我去便利店真的只是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一般我不会去做这种没有必要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直遵循既定的轨迹生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有必要？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也正是因此 像今天这样有空出来时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反而不知道该做些什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你觉得这种活法幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愁吃穿的富足生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该比任何人都幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那请你笑得再更幸福一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从一开始我就感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这家伙偶尔会露出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非常失落的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「没必要」还真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和你就是在这种「没必要」的时间里相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在便利店相遇 又跑来饭店吃荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小两口拌嘴？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:44.81,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我比你想象中的更想 更想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}劈腿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}情感泥潭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我是很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}饱了 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}气人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫名地气人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.30,0:18:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「没必要」的时间真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让你请客真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没能让你开心真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亚丽莎 亚丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上来就直接喊我名字 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别跟着我 别和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我现在正在气头上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求你了 消消气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.68,0:18:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起 原谅我没过脑子的胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你跑过来叫住我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}特意追过来 还跑了一身汗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过来把我叫住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实我也很想再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回想那次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你害羞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 这次笑得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等于是在说「我喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么说到底 亚丽莎也喜欢那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁让那个人神秘兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不知道整天在想啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有为什么一声不吭地就跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那意思是嫌我一股子山药泥味呗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有妇之夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呃 真要是这样就都白搭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}算了 反正他不来找我 我也没法再见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}随缘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}失落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}花岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是透有了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一次约会时咱们一定要去捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这还用说吗 必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}姜汁烧肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好棒耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}照吃不误
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也要我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也要吃肉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不够还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那什么 今天大家去哪儿玩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小透 你不怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感动极了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感动？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在鬼屋里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可把我累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在光是回想起来眼泪已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗 这鬼屋还真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过也好 暑假伊始大家开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}暑假才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像今天这样开心又激动我还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果能一直看着你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我定会永远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:41.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果能碰触你的双唇的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回来了吗 红野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没在外面做什么不该做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请放心 慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.81,0:22:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或许今后再没有机会见到你了吧
